{"type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      \"As Seen In\" Press Bar + Upgraded Testimonials\n      Two-layer approach: A slim credibility bar near the top of the page (after the booking bar) showing \"SF Chronicle • Tri-City Voice\" — instant authority signal. Then the best press quotes replace 2 of the 4 anonymous testimonials, interspersed through the page with publication attribution.\n      \n        Page flow:\n        Hero → Booking Bar → ★ Press Bar (NEW) → What Happened → ★ Press Quote (replaces testimonial) → Fragmented Memories → What Exactly Is This → ★ Press Quote (replaces testimonial) → Creators → Philosophy → Player Testimonial → FAQ → Player Testimonial → Booking Widget","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773954029393}
